    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn19.16:1.1",
          "pli": "“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, gijjhakūṭā pabbatā orohanto addasaṃ asīsakaṃ kabandhaṃ vehāsaṃ gacchantaṃ. ",
          "en": "“Just now, reverend, as I was descending from Vulture’s Peak Mountain I saw a headless trunk flying through the air. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.16:1.2",
          "pli": "Tassa ure akkhīni ceva honti mukhañca. ",
          "en": "Its eyes and mouth were on its chest. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.16:1.3",
          "pli": "Tamenaṃ gijjhāpi kākāpi kulalāpi anupatitvā anupatitvā vitacchenti virājenti. ",
          "en": "Vultures, crows, and hawks kept chasing it, pecking and clawing "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.16:1.4",
          "pli": "So sudaṃ aṭṭassaraṃ karoti … pe … ",
          "en": "as it screamed in pain. …” … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.16:1.5",
          "pli": "eso, bhikkhave, satto imasmiṃyeva rājagahe hāriko nāma coraghātako ahosi … pe …. ",
          "en": "“That being used to be an executioner called Hārika right here in Rājagaha. …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn19.16:1.6",
          "pli": "Chaṭṭhaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
